# ── macOS junk ───────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# ── Build output (regenerable; never commit signed binaries) ──
native/build/
*.app
*.dSYM
# legacy Go-era output (kept so old trees stay clean)
/bin/
/dist/
*.test
coverage.out

# ── Private working memory & internal docs (NEVER publish) ───
# These hold the developer's email, name, location, chat history,
# and internal vulnerability notes. They must never reach GitHub.
.claude/
CLAUDE.md
AUDIT.md
PLAN-2.0.md

# ── Design mockups (contain machine-specific demo data) ──────
design/
*.dc.html

# ── Local user config / personal denylist (machine-specific) ─
*.local
.maccleaner/
denylist.json

# ── Internal security audits — NEVER publish (hold vuln notes + real paths) ─
*cold-audit*.md
MacCleaner-cold-audit-*.md

# ── Internal publishing guide (contains the maintainer's local path) ─
GITHUB_PUBLISH_GUIDE.md
